txt.en: Many kinds of insects and spiders can be found in Lhingris.\n\nYou should defeat spiders and insects.
Atli Spider-bane has requested that any adventurers travelling to Lhingris should destroy all the spiders they come across.

An angry note hangs on the board, signed by Atli Spider-bane:

'Wanted: Spiders Dead!
If you travel into Lhingris, kill all the Shelob-spawn you can find! This includes all spider-kind and any other dangerous insects.'
